{"tid":1815172,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"我地反達小隊正式宣布退出抗爭","createTime":"2020-01-07T10:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T02:06:04.000Z","uid":37875,"like":32,"dislike":82,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"8e86a500d39ef77890a97b6414328128a4505ba2","tid":1815172,"uid":37875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:10:05.000Z","msg":"我地係一班曾經好嬲達哥既兄弟<br />\n但係當我地冷靜落黎之後就開始反思<br />\n其實達哥暗示過自己係黃<br />\n加上見到達哥既片依然好多人睇<br />\n令我地更加懷疑自己反達係咪少數<br />\n經過深思熟慮同反覆討論之後<br />\n我地決定不再反達 <br />\n做返達太祖&lt;3既真兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c438f719b4a14e5b1136e7ba1872892c303e6c90","tid":1815172,"uid":32454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:10:28.000Z","msg":"係 唔再反達lu"},{"pid":"1930b44dfe1f774e7d742956d991670a6c16a607","tid":1815172,"uid":3696,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:12:05.000Z","msg":"過氣啦 無人玩㗎啦-.-<br />\n引戰狗"},{"pid":"4476157a5a97b462a26a3137f74f69b8f92042f2","tid":1815172,"uid":258649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:14:20.000Z","msg":"Who<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d1e2cbf1204346114f05c39aace2d0cff083960","tid":1815172,"uid":37875,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c438f719b4a14e5b1136e7ba1872892c303e6c90","tid":1815172,"uid":32454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:10:28.000Z","msg":"係 唔再反達lu"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:22:06.000Z","msg":"反吾落了"},{"pid":"40ee2d193fcfbc0b58a9d86b5483927e707ec419","tid":1815172,"uid":37875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4476157a5a97b462a26a3137f74f69b8f92042f2","tid":1815172,"uid":25